OL,7,FA woman from Swindon who was conned
OL,8,Fout of #75,000 by a rogue trader says
OL,9,Fhis sub-standard work left her with a
OL,10,Fcollapsed ceiling, and her son
OL,11,Fsleeping in a mouldy bedroom.
OL,13,FJane, whose name has been changed to
OL,14,Fprotect her identity, hired Kerry
OL,15,FSharland to build a new kitchen,
OL,16,Fbedroom and bathroom for her family.
