OL,4,Cbuilder who left her with collapsed
OL,5,Cceiling
OL,7,FShe is one of four couples who fell
OL,8,Fvictim to his substandard work, before
OL,9,Fhe was convicted in August 2024 of
OL,10,Ffraudulent trading and given a two
OL,11,Fyear suspended sentence.
OL,13,FJane was left with no option but to
OL,14,Ffork out #100,000 to fix it.
OL,16,FAfter two weeks of work on the house,
OL,17,FJane said he began to give excuses for
OL,18,Fnot turning up to work, or claimed
OL,19,Ftradespeople were delayed.
