OL,7,FBy winter, heavy rain and snow had
OL,8,Fcaused the ceiling to collapse with
OL,9,Fwheelie bins and buckets used to
OL,10,Fcollect dripping water inside the
OL,11,Fhouse.
OL,13,F"You couldn't even really feel
OL,14,Fcomfortable going out for the day
OL,15,Fbecause you had to be in to empty the
OL,16,Fbuckets," said Jane.
OL,18,F"You don't realise the stress, the
OL,19,Fpressure it puts you under. It's just
OL,20,Ftakes over your life..."
