OL,4,Cbuilder who left her with collapsed
OL,5,Cceiling
OL,7,FKerry Sharland, Director of KS
OL,8,FBuilding & Renovations Limited, was
OL,9,Fsentenced at Swindon Crown Court on 29
OL,10,FAugust following an investigation by
OL,11,FSwindon Borough Council's Trading
OL,12,FStandards team.
OL,14,FThe 50-year-old admitted to a charge
OL,15,Fof fraudulent trading under the
OL,16,FCompanies Act 2006. The case involved
OL,17,Ffour couples who signed contracts with
OL,18,FSharland to do various building work
OL,19,Ffor them. Another couple like Jane had
OL,20,Ftheir ceiling collapse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
